title: Solo/Duo partner wanted from B1 - S1
body:
Hey guys,

Looking for a chill dude to climb the solo/duo ladder with me starting at Bronze 1(since that is where I am at).
You shouldn't mind losing because it is going to happen at least a little bit.
Let me know what your main roles are if you are interested.


P.S. As unlikely as it is if there is a high elo player with a low elo account if you would be kind enough to see if i'm worth your time that would be awesome LOL.
